The paper deals with the prediction of physical attributes from facial images using Convolutional Neural Networks. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep learning models for prediction also suggests the possibility of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) being a relevant sub-category. The dataset used in the paper was crawled from the web, which could also suggest multimedia (cs.MM) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with image-based prediction, which could also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
